  06 Oct 2003; Martin Holzer <mholzer@gentoo.org> openquicktime-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  fixed typo. PROVIDES -> PROVIDE.

  02 Oct 2003; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org>
  openquicktime-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Made it PROVIDE virtual/quicktime and block if it's present due to bug 27851.

  10 Jun 2003; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org>
  openquicktime-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed bug 22186 - missing dependency

*openquicktime-1.0-r1 (14 Apr 2003)

  14 Apr 2003; Martin Holzer <mholzer@gentoo.org> Manifest,
